                                    mailcat

Mailcat is a program that will listen on a designated port and receive emails
printing to stdout.

It is still mainly a work in progress, but is a tool I'm working on for work
to log emails from our applications


EXAMPLE

while true; do
  mailcat 25 > "./logs/"$(date +%s)
done

